author: wn.com
title: With no takers on pilot program, officials to revisit airport ride-booking rules
text: Five weeks after a ride-booking pilot project launched that requires fingerprint background checks for drivers in popular services such as Lyft and Uber to operate at the airport, San Jose has seen no takers and on Monday officials moved toward taking a new look at the issue. ...
